data.description:
Welcome to a residence that epitomizes timeless sophistication and refined living. This graceful patio home is ready for your immediate closing and occupancy, offering a perfect marriage of luxury and easy upkeep. Throughout the home, a subdued and elegant color palette creates an atmosphere of enduring style.

As you enter, be captivated by the voluminous living room adorned with plantation shutters, a hassle-free gas log fireplace, and exquisite built-ins. The private patio, nestled in a manageable yard, beckons for moments of quiet relaxation. The second living area, a versatile space, can be your home office, sanctuary, or creative retreat.

Retreat to the primary bedroom, a haven of tranquility with abundant space, dual walk-in closets, and a spa-like en-suite. Indulge in the jetted tub and appreciate the expansive vanity counters. 

The skylit gourmet kitchen, with ample storage—and even room for an island—is a culinary delight.

Safety is paramount, and the in-ground storm shelter in the two-car garage provides peace of mind during storm seasons. The private courtyard outside sets the stage for enchanting evenings under the stars or perhaps a soothing hot tub in your future. For added convenience, Shawnee Country Club's amenities are just steps away.

Live a life of refined luxury in this exceptional home, where every detail speaks to a mature and discerning taste. Embark on a virtual journey of opulence and sophistication—explore every detail in our exclusive 360º tour and envision your life of luxury in this exquisite residence.
